# Feature Architecture

Each feature must follow this structure:

```
features/<feature-name>/
    data/
        dto/
        api/
        repository/
        mapper/
    domain/
        model/
        repository/
        usecase/
    presentation/
        state/
        viewmodel/
        ui/
```

Rules:

- domain must not depend on data
- DTOs exist only in data layer
- repositories map DTO -> domain
- ViewModel uses UseCases
- UI consumes ViewModel state

Always generate for a new feature:

- DTO
- Mapper
- Repository
- UseCase
- ViewModel
- Compose Screen
- DI module wiring
